{"tid":1886680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失戀好痛 抖唔到氣","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T00:09:14.000Z","uid":163743,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"46a579d31a82d3fa495152a7617082bf98ec9bba","tid":1886680,"uid":163743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"係咪要即刻搵另一個對象先可以忘記到？<br />\n痛到想辭職，收埋自己一個，<br />\n唔想面對依個世界，<br />\n初初淨係話同朋友傾閒計既你，<br />\n你同第二個男人出街既時候係咪好開心？<br />\n俾人flirt個種感覺，暪住我，係咪好刺激？<br />\n<br />\n你身邊既朋友都知，你屋企人都知，係我唔知。"},{"pid":"eb950ca0c48a1e9d243afcf4a03c35f1d72a62f0","tid":1886680,"uid":54189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾人背叛既感覺真係好震撼"},{"pid":"57ca6d8691d748c43092f0e7cc7d270dbb07a538","tid":1886680,"uid":198130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"放眼看 一切隨緣 聽下佛經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b3591f3e68179a939326896a91f1a4a8d11d30","tid":1886680,"uid":235637,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"你條女應該好中意刺激<br />\n<br />\n可能日日畀條仔屌到出晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3da8abc448b88e5e6a2ec0df750c10f7753eaa3","tid":1886680,"uid":198130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"有時候我們放不開不是因為失去，而是心疼自己的付出。遺忘的好處是：也許會後悔，也許會難過，但是心卻不會再疼。曾經看不慣，受不了的，如今不過淡然一笑。成熟，不是看破，而是看淡。"},{"pid":"60fafa2fe02b33975c418be1ae5727012a757137","tid":1886680,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab2a5df5fc82a0426339994249659f10703cf5e","tid":1886680,"uid":53553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"