,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T20:35:29.000Z","msg":"失戀的必經階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都試過 真係好辛苦<br />\n支持住呀...<br />\n捱過呢段最艱難嘅時間<br />\n之後就會好啲架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4923f44f3f3245ba033d54293a043c358b024ac6","tid":1886680,"uid":2903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:09:14.000Z","msg":"我好過你<br />\n分咗一排放底咗先知<br />\n未分嗰陣已經有新對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}